window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>For the first time ever, we've collected all three books in the Monster Girl Safari saga for this special omnibus edition.</b></p> <p><b>Love. Honor. Family. </b></p> <p>Follow Luke as he's transported to a world of magic and monsters. A mysterious goddess has tasked the Earthly game warden with protecting an all-female tribe with strange animal features. Cast off from civilization, he must help this isolated jungle people fortify their village against the rapacious Rakhasa, confound a wicked witch, and breed the next generation of monster children.</p>"; 
